title: Fruits'n Tails v1
description:
GET READY TO DISCOVER THE REAL SECRET OF DA VINCI!

Leonardo da Vinci is in a creative block when he finds a map that leads him to a mysterious mountain, where he meets the colorful monkeys and gets their help painting a new portrait.

Use Ticelli, Vince, Ludovico and Sanzio to pick up the fruits in the forest, make paint with the fruits and help the genious Leonardo Da Vinci painting his ultimate masterpiece.
